description:
Resident Evil Village: Gold Edition includes the base game with three additional major new features:

- Third Person Mode, which allows the players to play the main story mode from a new perspective;
- The Mercenaries Additional Orders, introducing new playable characters and stages;
- Shadows of Rose, a story DLC continuing the story of Ethan's daughter, Rosemary.
